Version 1.1
Release Date: June 2013

This is the README file for the CORBATA(Core Biome Analysis Tool).

Released packages can be downloaded from SourceForge.net:
	http://sourceforge.net/projects/corbata/

Additional information may be found at:
	http://www.jcvi.org/cms/research/projects/corbata


Distribution Structure
======================

NOTE: Please use the Unix command "tar -xvf Corbata_<release_date>.tgz" to uncompress the tar package.

README		--	This file
doc/         	-- 	Documentation regarding how to run scripts and description of outputs
lib/		--	Standalone and other miscellaneous scripts
example_data/	--	Example input files
example_run/	--	Example scripts for invoking analyses
Run_Single_SampleAnalyses.pl	--  Run through suite of single cohort analyses
Run_Two_SampleComparisons.pl	--  Run through suite of two cohort comparison analyses

Run the two above scripts to display usage and capabilities.
